<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:820px">
    <div class="guide-toc">
      <h4>In this guide</h4>
      <a href="#why">Why it happens</a>
      <a href="#matters">Why it matters more than it looks</a>
      <a href="#fix">Fixing it by hand</a>
      <a href="#software">How software keeps games fresh</a>
      <a href="#faq">Frequently asked questions</a>
